Description: inline doc strings for Annotated[] (Avalan PPA transitive)
 annotated-doc is a small helper for attaching documentation to
 typing.Annotated parameters and return types. Packaged for the
 Avalan PPA because fastapi requires `>= 0.0.2` and the package is
 not in Debian. Zero runtime dependencies.
